column3: Superb fast and classy phone with a great camera
column5: I ordered the 32 GB iPhone 7 via Amazon. The phone arrived on time and well packed. The phone was absolutely new and the manufacturing date was as recent asOctober 2018 itself.  The phone is definitely an excellent upgrade over the iPhone 6 and 6s. It comes pre loaded with iOS 12.0.1 and is extremely fast and zippy. The built of the phone is superb and it feels extremely premium. The camera is amazing and the sound quality is loud with a clear output. Overall an excellent phone.

iPhone is a great device, because of the tight integration of hardware and software. This is my second iPhone and I have purchased it on 2018 (2 yrs after release) because I think 40,000 is max I am willing to spend on this device.

This is a still a phone worth buying in 2018. Apple still has the best LCD display in the market. Sound quality is great. Phone is lag free because of the constant updates from Apple. This is one of the important reasons why you should buy an iPhone. When both the hardware and software is managed by the same company you can expect the phone to keep up with time unlike many other phone manufacturers who stop with out of the box software. The main con is battery life. To provide a sleek phone Apple cuts on battery size and hence don’t expect too much of on screen time if you’re a gaming enthusiast or watch a lot of videos on phone. The stand by time however is great because of the latest software update. Overall a good phone to experience the Apple space.
Switching from android to iOS was a mistake

Compared to the price the features and the quality that iPhones offer now make them too over priced. Also, Apple is not at all bothered about the Indian market. Apple maps does not support directions and other important search features. iPhone always need WiFi to backup and install apps larger than 150 MB. Now when I get 40 GB per month, of 4g data, for a plan of ~300 rupees why should I bother about WiFi.

column3: Great iPhone with all the latest features at an unbelievable price
column5: The Apple iPhone 7 (Black) is a step ahead from the previous iPhones. I previously used the iPhone 6 and this one has a lot many new features like 3D Touch, Force Touch, Live Photos and the phone is a lot more faster too. The new iOS works swift and fast and is very suitable for the the 7. Amazon offered a great deal on the phone during Diwali and I got it for about 37,500. Amazon delivery was straight up; the phone was seal packed and retains the apple 1 year warranty. The matte black is a great colour, relatively harder to scratch than the jet black version too. This one has a very subtle look to it; un-exagerated and un-boastful in appearance.

column3: In love with my new iPhone7
column5: Phone is awesome. Phone design, look is great. Someone said Apple 2 GB RAM = Android 4 GB RAM. It’s true.Apple camera clarity is really good. apps loading time is very quick and so fast. Battery back up is satisfactory. I’m continually using mobile with Mobil data on, phone could long last for 1 1/2 day. Fingerprints sensor is very fast & accurate . It protects even Paytm wallet. display is good. EarPods are amazing. Love you apple .

The apple still the best of the best. This is my 3rd iPhone. iPhone 6 iPhone se then this black diamond Jet Black. Speed. Beauty. Screen and camera as expected top of the line . The phone is very sleepery due to so slim and glass back and smuge magnet. I am using it for a month now no issue at all. And we all seen the security of android data breaches. Latest addition is one plus. But in iPhone just buy and forget. This 32 GB model is not for them who use heavy songs game and content download. Those go for higher GB model. I hate anything anyphone more then 5" size. Although the Samsung s series has given great competition. But in compact size and security issues apple has beaten them hands down. The battery is great. I am a heavy internet user. Who uses more then 1 GB per day. But in a day one full charge is enough for my needs. And one more important issue no heating at all and fingerprint scanner in front is a big deal to me. So apple keep up the good job.

Always buying stuff from cloudtail , geniune seller. Also nothing much to add as iPhone 7 has met with all the expectations I had. Luckily I bought before pre GST sale....so bought under good deal. If you're looking to use this phone for more than 2 years than opt for 128 GB and not 32 GB
